Recommended Tech Stack
Frontend

React.js or Next.js (you're already comfortable with these)
TypeScript for type safety
Tailwind CSS for rapid UI development
Shadcn UI or Material-UI for components

Backend

Django REST Framework (leverages your Django experience) OR Node.js with Express
PostgreSQL for relational data
Redis for caching and session management

Authentication & Security

JWT tokens
OAuth 2.0 for SSO integration
Role-based access control (RBAC)

File Storage

AWS S3 or Cloudinary for document management

Real-time Features

WebSockets for notifications
Django Channels or Socket.io

Deployment

Docker for containerization
AWS/Azure or Railway for hosting
CI/CD with GitHub Actions

